HEADWORD: Predicability
<hw>Pred`i*ca*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
or state of being predicable, or affirmable of something, or attributed
to something.</def> <rj><au>Reid.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

